        "Id": "mechdef_terminus_TMS-S2",
        "Name": "Terminus",
        "Details": "Clan Diamond Shark followed up the Rampart, its first superheavy BattleMech, with the Terminus. Learning their lessons from the earlier design, the clan's designers gave the Terminus an all-energy-weapon loadout: this removes the risk of ammunition explosions, and is also better at dealing with light, agile opposition. The 'Mech's electronics remain top-notch, with the centerpiece being a Nova CEWS sourced from the clan's allies. The TMS-2 replaces the standard ER PPCs with the recently developed Refined Plasma PPCs, somewhat increasing the damage but reducing the overall range.<br><br>S-class mechs feature upgrades to their armour, thermal management and defensive systems that substantially improve their survivability on the 31st century battlefield.",
